<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a8ee41e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8711"><num value="8711">§ 8711.</num><heading> Amendments to orders</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this chapter applicable to the order shall be applicable to any amendment to the order, except that <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s8707">section 8707 of this title</ref> shall not apply to an amendment.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a8ee41f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/115/254/dE/s1312">Pub. L. 115–254, div. E, § 1312</ref>, <date date="2018-10-05">Oct. 5, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/3483">132 Stat. 3483</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
